---
import SectionTitle from './common/SectionTitle.astro';
---

<section id="about" class="mx-auto max-w-[1080px] scroll-mt-20 px-7 pb-[clamp(64px,9vw,110px)]">
  <SectionTitle prefix="01" label="about"/>

  <div class="max-w-[62ch]">
    <p class="text-[clamp(17px,2vw,22px)] font-medium leading-[1.65] text-fg">
      I'm a fullstack developer in Calgary with a background in 
      <span class="text-accent">
      ERP systems, backend automation, and business-critical software. 
      </span>
      I've spent the last few years building the kind of software that quietly 
      keeps a company running — warehouse systems, supply chain tooling, financial controls, and more.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-5 text-[15px] leading-[1.8] text-muted">
      I started as the first developer at CRL Synergy — no team, no playbook, just operational problems that 
      needed solving. Today I lead a team of six and have shipped solutions across warehousing, supply chain, 
      accounting, QA, and more.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
